<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1361504" n="1"/>
<opener>Viro <abbr>Ill.<hi rend="sup">mo</hi></abbr> et <abbr>Eruditiss.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolao Bernoulli</rs>
<lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Petrus Antonius Michelotti</rs></opener>
<p><lb/>Quod adversa etiamnum fruare valetudine (quemadmo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dum tuis <rs key="B_991170517051805501" type="letter">literis</rs> <add>nuper</add> mihi nunciasti) doleo et moleste fero Vir
                              <lb/>Amicissime. Si gravitate stomachi, repletione aut nau<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sea citra febrim, laboras non opus erit ut voces aliquem
                              <lb/>ex istis Medicis. Recipe octo pilulas quas h<choice><orig><g ref="#ihat">î</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice>c seiunc<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tim Tibi pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>scribo, dimidia hora ante parcam c<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>am.
                              <lb/>H<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> pilul<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> purgabunt superfluitates sine perturbatio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ne sanguinis, iisque uti poteris pro re nata deci<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ma quinta quaque die tuend<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> valetudinis grati<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>,
                              <lb/>quam tibi firmissimam<del> pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cor</del><add> de</add>precor. Tibi gratias
                              <lb/>refero pro iis qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ad me dedisti circa calculos <rs key="pers_DE-588-124275087" type="person">Keillia 
                              <lb/>nos</rs>, quorum rationem deinceps inibo, et si quas invene<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ro difficultates ad Te confugiam. Circa <date><add>hujus</add> mensis fin<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice></date>
<lb/>spero parata me habere omnia qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> mittenda duxi
                              <lb/>ad <abbr>Celeber.</abbr> Patruum Tuum <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Joannem</rs>: quapropter ex<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>pectabo responsa quum advenient <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basil<choice><orig><g ref="#ehat">ê</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice>a</rs>. De <rs key="pers_DE-588-120379260" type="person">Scheuc<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>hzero</rs> nostro Amicissimo h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c habeo Tibi dicendo.<note type="internal"><!-- ToDo: Kontrollieren, ob "dicendo" korrekt. --></note> Persis<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tit adhuc <choice><orig><g ref="#AE">Æ</g></orig><reg>Ae</reg></choice>ques (de quo Tibi constat) in opinione contra<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dicendi; ideoque <abbr>Excell.</abbr> <rs type="person">Paschalius</rs> <choice><sic>operat</sic><corr>operas</corr></choice> dat ut eum a
                              <lb/>proposito<del> bland</del> le<unclear>n</unclear>iter removeat. Dedi ipsi <rs type="person">Paschali<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>co</rs> omnia qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> continentur in <rs type="keyword">Commentariis</rs> <abbr>Academ.</abbr>
<lb/><abbr>Reg.</abbr> <rs key="place_GEO-2988507" type="place"><abbr>Paris.</abbr></rs> et rationes multas ipsi subministravi
                              <lb/>quibus promotionem justissimam <rs key="pers_DE-588-120379260" type="person">Scheuchzeri</rs> tueri
                              <pb facs="1361505" n="2"/>
<lb/>valeat. Hoc ut scribas velim <rs key="pers_DE-588-120379260" type="person">Scheuchzero</rs> meoque no<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mine eidem salutem plurimam mittas rogando ut
    <lb/>quam citissime fieri poterit mittat ad me <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_FTUNNEH6">Astro<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>graphiam</rs> non modo, sed et <rs key="pers_DE-588-118607308" type="person">Fratris</rs> sui dissertatio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nes <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_UMPBVAXH">de Cerva cornuta</rs>, <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_IH5TP3NW">de surdo Audiente</rs>, <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_28S3J68W">de 
        <lb/>Usu Matheseos in Medicina</rs>, et omnia qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Ty<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>pis <add>idem</add> mandavit. Etenim de hisce locutus sum
    <lb/><abbr>Excell.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1089922930">Paschalium</rs> qui pluribus studet promo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tionem tueri et Senatus authoritate confir<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mare.</p> <closer><salute>Vale Vir <abbr>Clariss.</abbr> et me amare perge.</salute>
    <lb/>Dabam <rs key="place_VER-repven" type="place">Venetiis</rs> <choice><abbr>a. d.</abbr><expan>a dato</expan></choice> <date when="1718-11-14">14 Nov.<hi rend="sup">bris</hi> 1718.</date></closer> <note hand="pers_DE-588-119166895"><foreign xml:lang="ger"><abbr>Empf.en</abbr> den <date when="1718-11-15">15.<hi rend="sup">ten</hi> <abbr>9.bris</abbr></date></foreign></note>
<postscript><p><lb/><abbr>P. S.</abbr>
<lb/>Gratissimum mihi fuit quod nunciasti de <abbr>Clari<unclear>ss.</unclear></abbr>
    <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117589144">Patruele</rs> Tuo, quem uti summo semper prosequar
                              <lb/>amore, ita ipsum honoribus, dignitatibus <add>muneribusque</add> deinceps
                              <lb/>affici mirifice gaudebo. Saluta eum meo nomine
                              <lb/>quum ad eum scribes. <choice><orig>jubes</orig><reg>Jubes</reg></choice> enim ut nihil ad
    <lb/>eum scribam donec ipse aut <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Pater</rs> ejus de mihi
                              <lb/>nunciata electione certiorem faciant. Peto interim
                              <lb/>annon possim de<del> hac</del><del> ist</del> illa electione verba facere
                              <lb/>h<choice><orig><g ref="#ihat">î</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice>c coram meis Proceribus et Amicis. C<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terum
                              <lb/>Te moneo, <abbr>Excell.</abbr> <rs type="person">Paschalicum</rs> mihi plura de istis
                              <lb/>Professoribus male sentientibus de Germanis et pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice><pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sertim de <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-120379260">Scheuchzero</rs> et de Te, communicasse. Ad qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
                              <pb facs="1361507" n="3"/>
<lb/>ego multa respondi pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sertim circa<del> usum</del> lingu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> latin<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
                              <lb/>(quam Vos <add>non</add> possidere falso <add>isti</add> pronunciant) usum in
                              <lb/>rebus Mathematicis et Botanicis pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ter qu<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> quod
                              <lb/>ei testatus sum Vos revera Latine loqui et equi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dem emendate, immo vero posse elegantissime,
                              <lb/>si quidem opus esset, scribere. Plura adjeci, <subst><del>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></del><add>de quibus</add></subst> coram
                              <lb/>bacanalibus proximis Deo favente loquemur. In<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/><gap/><note type="editorial">Hier folgt eine grössere Lakune wegen ausgeschnittenem Papier.</note>
<lb/>epistolam.</p></postscript>
</div>
